.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: golf, parkour, basketball, skateboarding, handball
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, dahlia, iris, daffodil
1. the british is the person who likes red
2. the swedish is the person who growsdahlia
3. the danish is the person who's sport is skateboarding
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person who's sport is parkour
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who growsamaryllis
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growstulip
11. the person who growsdaffodils is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's sport is golf
13. the german is the prince-smoker
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Flower		|     tulip	|    daffodil	|     amaryllis	|     iris	|      dahlia	|
| Sport	|    handball	|     skateboarding	|     basketball	|    parkour	|      golf	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
